title: Kim Dae-won (footballer, born 1992)
text: Daewon Kim (born 24 April 1992) is a former professional <a href="South%20Korea">South Korean</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>, who last played for <a href="FK%20Pardubice">FK Pardubice</a> in the <a href="Czech%20National%20Football%20League">Czech National Football League</a>.
